<template>
  <!-- <PlanCardList :plans='plans' /> -->
  <!-- <PlanSelectList :plans='plans' /> -->
  <!-- <PlanExpandList :plans='plans' /> -->
  <PlanTabList :plans='plans' />
</template>

<script>
import PlanCardList from '@/components/PlanCardList'
import PlanSelectList from '@/components/PlanSelectList'
import PlanExpandList from '@/components/PlanExpandList'
import PlanTabList from '@/components/PlanTabList'
import axios from 'axios'

export default {
  name: 'PlanView',
  components: {
    PlanCardList,
    PlanSelectList,
    PlanExpandList,
    PlanTabList,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      plans: []
    }
  },
  mounted() {
    this.getPlans()
    document.title = 'Home | Digital Wave'
  },
  methods: {
    async getPlans() {
      await axios
        .get('api/v1/plans/')
        .then(response => {
          this.plans = response.data
          console.log('plan data:', this.plans)
        })
        .catch(error => {
          console.log(error)
        })
    },
  }
}
</script>
